Demonstration of the Space-time FEM for two prominent classes of PDEs (parabolic, hyperbolic) and comparison with time-stepping methods.

The Jupyter notebooks are the supplementary materials to the article "Tutorial on Space-time FEM with FEniCSx" 
doi:	 10.5281/zenodo.16761463
url:	 https://zenodo.org/records/16761463

Tested with
Python 		3.12.9
fenics-dolfinx 	0.9.0
pyvista 	0.45.3

Author: Dominik Kern
https://orcid.org/0000-0002-1958-2982
